  {
    "index": 3,
    "hash": "Jio3s9Nwd471a+nbZWGdS1p3GFc=",
    "timestampUtcMs": "2026-05-13T13:00:40.000Z",
    "action": {
      "type": "SET_CONTENT",
      "input": {
        "content": "# Per-User Operation Feed\n\nIn collaborative mode, each user writes their own operations to `ph:v2:ops:<address>:<docId>`, owned by that user's signer. Peers read each other's op feeds.\n\n## Schema\n\n```json\n{\n  \"type\": \"operations\",\n  \"channelMeta\": { \"source\": \"0xAlice_signer\" },\n  \"operations\": [\n    {\n      \"operation\": {\n        \"id\": \"op-aaa\",\n        \"index\": 0,\n        \"skip\": 0,\n        \"timestampUtcMs\": \"1712750460000\",\n        \"hash\": \"abc123...\",\n        \"action\": { \"id\": \"act-001\", \"type\": \"ADD_LINE_ITEM\", \"scope\": \"global\" }\n      },\n      \"context\": {\n        \"documentId\": \"doc-001\",\n        \"documentType\": \"powerhouse/budget-statement\",\n        \"scope\": \"global\",\n        \"branch\": \"main\",\n        \"ordinal\": 1\n      }\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n## Key points\n\n- Each feed index is one batch, debounced\n- `channelMeta.source` identifies the writer for downstream validation\n- `context.ordinal` is the writer-local sequence number \u2014 NOT the globally-resolved index\n- Final global index/skip is assigned by each reader's reactor during conflict resolution\n",
        "updatedAt": "2026-05-13T13:00:40.000Z"
      },
      "timestampUtcMs": "2026-05-13T13:00:40.000Z"
    }
  },
